install dependency:
    pip install -r requirements.txt
usage:
	python manage.py

-----------------------------------------
strcture:
|-flasky
    |-app/
        |-templates/
        |-static/
        |-main/
            |-__init__.py
            |-errors.py
            |-forms.py
            |-views.py
        |-__init__.py
        |-email.py
        |-models.py
    |-migrations/
    |-tests/
        |-__init__.py
        |-test*.py
    |-venv/
    |-requirements.txt
    |-config.py
    |-manage.py

-----------------------------------------
basic function:
search blank: search for the blog based on the keywords
explore: the recently published blog,or recommand problem
Home: write your blog
Blog: to show all the Blog and your friends blog
Comment:write your comment
Follow:follow the guys that you interested

----------------------------------------
the navigation bar:
Home:to get the newest post your friends published
Blog:to write your own blog
Explore: to provide "search" and "I'm feeling something"
userInfo: the show the information and log in,log out
private_message: to notify the message you have receive

----------------------------------------
extra information:
write the dependency to a txt:   pip freeze > requirements.txt
